Westley Capper has admitted driving Agnese Klavina away from nightclub Aqwa Mist in Puerto Banus . 
  The 30-year-old waitress disappeared after a night out at the club on September 6 last year . 
  Capper refused to be questioned by police and co-accused Craig Porter also refused to answer questions in court . 
  Cappers and Porter have both admitted being in the Mercedes with her before she vanished . 
  Authorities are probing possibility she was killed and her body thrown into the sea . 
 